data.description: Move-in ready ranch home with a large upstairs bonus room! This home offers an open concept living space. This home has 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths on the main level including the spacious primary suite & large primary bathroom with a great walk-in closet, this home also features a large kitchen, breakfast area, large great room looking out to the the covered porch perfect for outdoor entertaining. Beautiful hardwood floors throughout the main level, carpet in BRs, tile in bathrooms, kitchen with granite counters, tile backsplash, island, pantry, all appliances included. Sprinkler system. Minutes to shops, restaurants and interstate and more!
